  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba 18\u0d9a \u0da2\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An 18-hour water cut for Colombo and many surrounding areas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board says that the water supply to many areas will be suspended for a period of 18 hours from 8.00 am on Saturday, 03 September to 02.00 am on Sunday, 04 September, due to the essential maintenance of the electricity supply to Ambatale water pumping station.",
        "The Water Supply Board further states that water supply will be suspended to Colombo, Dehiwala, Mount Kilissa, Kotte, Kaduwela Municipal Council areas, Maharagama, Boralasgamuwa, Kolonnawa Municipal Council areas, Kotikawatta, Mulleriya, Regional Council areas, Ratmalana and Katubedda. ."
      ],
